      "text": "The value of theory cannot be underestimated. In this paper I am focussing on the theoretical concept of ‘Boundary’. However, like Lewin’s (1951) assertion that “there is nothing as practical as a good theory” (p.169), I aim to explicitly discuss the practical implications of my research as I investigate the ontology of Boundary within the context of leadership in a networked world."
