      "text": "Pragmatically, the proposed research endeavours to build upon existing research on leadership in a complex and networked world using systemic thinking and the adoption of interactive technologies. Based on the results, I aim to deliver an easily deployable and practical systemic tool for leaders and managers to design, develop and implement sustainable interactive systems that can be deployed across social and business functions."
